'''Akomeye mu mutwe'''

Umuntu yitwa ko akomeye mu mutwe igihe ashobora gukora neza mu buzima bwa minsi yose, agakorana n’abandi, agafata ingingo, akagira ico aterera mu kibano, akamenya ingene yigenza mu bintu bigusagirije no mu bihe bigoye, akongera agashika kukunezerwa bikwiye. Indwara zo mu mutwe n’indwara zihungabanya amagara y’umuntu mu mutwe.

Impunzi zirakunda gufatwa n’indwara zo mu mutwe kubera ivyo zaciyemwo mu buzima bihahamura. Igihugu c’amavuko cabo kenshi kirakenye kandi nta mutekano ukiranga, bashobora kuba barahungabanirijwe ubuzima, barabuze canke barazimije ababo, canke bapfunzwe.

